### POST - Add Ballet Slippers
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "storeId": "dance-store-001",
    "storeName": "Flavia's Dance Shop",
    "productId": "d1",
    "productName": "Ballet Slippers",
    "price": 49.99
}

